<title>tḥt ẓlk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tḥt ẓlk yạ rby ạlḥbyb ạ̉sẖthy rby ạ̉bqy̱ mnk qryb
 (nfsy tfrḥ wqlby yṭyb krby ydẖhb wḥzny ygẖyb)2
 2-fy hdẖạ ạlwʿạr lys ly swạk ḥytẖ sẖkẖṣk mkạny hnạk
 (ḥytẖ ạ̉stṭyʿ bạ̹ymạny ạ̉rạk ḥytẖ tẓhr bạlḥb ly bhạk)2
 3- mʿ ạ̉kẖwty bsẖkẖṣk nḥyṭ wʿlmk hw ḥb sẖdyd
 (ạ̉nt qạỷd wrys mjyd ạ̉nt klk yạ rbnạ fryd)2
 4-ạ̉qrạṣ ạlzbyb tsnd ạltʿwb sẖkẖṣk ạlʿjyb ynʿsẖ ạlqlwb
 (wsẖmạlk tḥt rạ̉sy wymynk tnjd ạlmgẖlwb)2</lyrics>
</song>